Details:
Land/Use Occupancy for Industrial Roadway (Monkey Beach Forest Service Road & Kennedy Island roads).  The road will be used to allow access through the Conservancy to the cutting permit areas (outside of the Conservancy) for:
a) Timber harvesting operations & associated activities and inspections;
b) Silviculture operations including surveys, reforestation treatments such as tree planting;
c) Future timber development planning and engineering activities; and 
d) Road maintenance & deactivation operations.
